v2_18d596fe.original: How do I upgrade my plan?

v2_7653cb6c.original: You can upgrade through our website by visiting the pricing page and choosing your preferred plan. We use Stripe for secure payment processing and offer both monthly and annual billing options.
v2_7653cb6c.translation: Unaweza kuboresha kupitia tovuti yetu kwa kutembelea ukurasa wa bei na kuchagua mpango unaoupenda. Tunatumia Stripe kwa usindikaji salama wa malipo na tunatoa chaguo la malipo ya kila mwezi au kila mwaka.

v2_5696f774.original: Can I cancel my subscription anytime?
v2_5696f774.translation: Je, naweza kughairi usajili wangu wakati wowote?

v2_1bd65019.original: Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time through your account settings. Your premium features will remain active until the end of your current billing period. No hidden fees or commitments.
v2_1bd65019.translation: Ndio, unaweza kughairi usajili wako wakati wowote kupitia mipangilio ya akaunti yako. Vipengele vyako vya premium vitaendelea kufanya kazi hadi mwisho wa kipindi chako cha malipo cha sasa. Hakuna ada zilizofichwa au ahadi za muda mrefu.

v2_5a728a36.original: FluentAI is currently available for Google Chrome and Firefox. We are actively working on Safari support, and you can submit a feature request for other browsers through our feature request page.
v2_5a728a36.translation: FluentAI inapatikana kwa sasa kwa Google Chrome na Firefox. Tunafanya kazi kwa bidii kusaidia Safari, na unaweza kuwasilisha ombi la kipengele kwa vivinjari vingine kupitia ukurasa wetu wa maombi ya vipengele.

v2_18d8b75e.original: Is there a mobile app available?
v2_18d8b75e.translation: Je, kuna programu tumizi ya simu inayopatikana?

v2_18db3079.original: A mobile app is currently on our roadmap and under development. Stay tuned for updates! You can follow our progress and submit feature requests for specific mobile functionality through our feature request page.
v2_18db3079.translation: Programu ya simu ya mkononi iko kwenye mpango kazi wetu na inaendelea kutengenezwa. Endelea kufuatilia masasisho! Unaweza kufuatilia maendeleo yetu na kutuma maombi ya vipengele maalum vya programu ya simu kupitia ukurasa wetu wa maombi ya vipengele.

v2_355caa77.original: Does FluentAI slow down my browser?
v2_355caa77.translation: Je, FluentAI hupunguza kasi ya kivinjari changu?

v2_30d3bd3c.original: No, FluentAI is designed to be lightweight and efficient. It runs seamlessly in the background and only activates when you are using supported streaming platforms. The impact on browser performance is minimal.
v2_30d3bd3c.translation: Hapana, FluentAI imeundwa iwe nyepesi na yenye ufanisi. Inafanya kazi kwa urahisi bila kuzingatia mbele na huanzishwa tu unapotumia majukwaa ya utiririshaji yanayoungwa mkono. Athari kwenye utendakazi wa kivinjari ni ndogo kabisa.

v2_29b6494a.original: Key features include: instant word translations, detailed explanations, pronunciation guides, vocabulary tracking, flashcard creation (Anki integration), neural subtitles for better understanding, and progress analytics. Check our pricing page for a detailed comparison of features available in each plan.
v2_29b6494a.translation: Vipengele vikuu ni pamoja na: tafsiri za maneno papo hapo, maelezo ya kina, miongozo ya matamshi, ufuatiliaji wa msamiati, uundaji wa kadi za kumbukumbu (ujumuishaji na Anki), manukuu ya neva kwa uelewa bora, na uchanganuzi wa maendeleo. Angalia ukurasa wetu wa bei kwa kulinganisha kwa kina vipengele vinavyopatikana katika kila mpango.

v2_70c7c4e3.original: Do you have a free plan?

v2_0fd1cb67.original: Yes! We offer a free plan that lets you try out the core features. For unlimited access and advanced features, check out our paid plans on the pricing page.
v2_0fd1cb67.translation: Ndiyo! Tunatoa mpango wa bure unaokuwezesha kujaribu vipengele vya msingi. Kwa ufikiaji usio na kikomo na vipengele vya juu, angalia mipango yetu ya kulipia kwenye ukurasa wa bei.

v2_1566e7a8.original: What makes FluentAI different from other language learning tools?
v2_1566e7a8.translation: Ni nini kinachofanya FluentAI kuwa tofauti na zana nyingine za kujifunza lugha?

v2_542bb975.original: FluentAI turns your everyday entertainment into effective language lessons. Instead of structured lessons, you learn naturally through content you enjoy. Our AI-powered system provides context-aware translations and explanations, making learning more engaging and effective.
v2_542bb975.translation: FluentAI hubadili burudani yako ya kila siku kuwa masomo madhubuti ya lugha. Badala ya masomo yaliyopangwa rasmi, unajifunza kwa njia ya asili kupitia maudhui unayofurahia. Mfumo wetu wenye nguvu wa AI hutoa tafsiri na maelezo yanayozingatia muktadha, na kufanya mchakato wa kujifunza kuwa wa kuvutia zaidi na wenye ufanisi.

v2_548d3e48.original: FluentAI is a browser extension that helps you learn languages while watching videos. It automatically shows translations, explanations, and pronunciation guides for words and phrases in your target language as you watch content on platforms like YouTube, Netflix, Disney+, and Prime Video.
v2_548d3e48.translation: FluentAI ni kiendelezi (extension) cha kivinjari kinachokusaidia kujifunza lugha unapozitazama video. Kinaonyesha tafsiri, maelezo, na mwongozo wa matamshi kwa maneno na misemo ya lugha unayolenga moja kwa moja unapotazama maudhui kwenye majukwaa kama YouTube, Netflix, Disney+, na Prime Video.

v2_092c62d4.original: FluentAI supports all languages through our AI-powered translation system. While the quality may vary depending on the language pair, we continuously work on improving translations for all languages. The most common languages like English, Spanish, French, German, etc., typically have the highest quality translations.
v2_092c62d4.translation: FluentAI inasaidia lugha zote kupitia mfumo wetu wa kutafsiri unaoendeshwa na AI. Ingawa ubora unaweza kutofautiana kulingana na jozi ya lugha, tunafanya kazi kila mara kuboresha tafsiri za lugha zote. Lugha zinazotumika zaidi kama Kiingereza, Kihispania, Kifaransa, Kijerumani, n.k., kwa kawaida zina tafsiri za ubora wa juu zaidi.

v2_16c6908b.original: As you watch videos, FluentAI analyzes the subtitles in real-time and provides interactive learning features. You can click on any word to see its translation, explanation, and hear its pronunciation. The extension also helps you create flashcards and track your learning progress.
v2_16c6908b.translation: Unapotazama video, FluentAI inachanganua manukuu kwa muda halisi na hutoa vipengele vya ujifunzaji shirikishi. Unaweza kubofya neno lolote kuona tafsiri yake, maelezo na kusikiliza matamshi yake. Kiendelezi hiki pia hukusaidia kuunda kadi za kumbukumbu na kufuatilia maendeleo yako ya kujifunza.
